cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the problem of single-view place recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The authors propose the use of neural network architectures, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the authors evaluate their approach on a dataset and provide a video showing their results, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
